OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1772701496
OL,3,CPopular Jersey festival cancelled over
OL,4,Cmoney concerns
OL,6,FThis year's Wonky Town festival in
OL,7,FJersey has been cancelled, as
OL,8,Forganisers say they are "unable to
OL,9,Fmake the finances stack up".
OL,11,FPromoters stress the decision has been
OL,12,Fmade "to pause and focus on building
OL,13,Fsomething stronger and more
OL,14,Fsustainable for next year", promising
OL,15,F"we'll be back".
OL,17,FThey add that anyone who has already
OL,18,Fpurchased tickets for the two-day
OL,19,Fevent, which went on sale at the end
OL,20,Fof January, will receive an automatic
OL,21,Frefund to their payment card.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/5
