OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1772701496
OL,3,CPopular Jersey festival cancelled over
OL,4,Cmoney concerns
OL,6,FThe popular alternative music festival
OL,7,Fdrew thousands to Fort Regent's East
OL,8,FDitch in St Helier, featuring a range
OL,9,Fof DJ sets and dance anthems -
OL,10,Fincluding genres such as house and
OL,11,Ftechno.
OL,13,FIt was due to take place on Friday 5
OL,14,Fand Saturday 6 June, with
OL,15,F"establishing artists alongside
OL,16,Fcredible emerging talent" and a new
OL,17,FVIP area.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1772701496
OL,3,CPopular Jersey festival cancelled over
OL,4,Cmoney concerns
OL,6,FOrganisers say they wanted to "make
OL,7,FWonky Town substantially better than
OL,8,Fthe year before", but have concluded
OL,9,Fthey are unable to "deliver a
OL,10,Fcredible, high-quality line-up at an
OL,11,Faffordable ticket price", despite
OL,12,Fworking to reduce costs and with
OL,13,Fgovernment support.
OL,15,FThey conclude, "The overall financial
OL,16,Frisk remains too high to move forward
OL,17,Fresponsibly.
OL,19,F"Putting on a world-class event in
OL,20,FJersey is not cheap."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
