OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1772701496
OL,3,CPopular Jersey festival cancelled over
OL,4,Cmoney concerns
OL,6,FThe festival's organisers add: "Rather
OL,7,Fthan compromise on quality or take
OL,8,Frisks that could damage the festival
OL,9,Flong-term, we're choosing to pause and
OL,10,Ffocus on building something stronger
OL,11,Fand more sustainable for next year."
OL,13,FFans have been quick to express their
OL,14,Fdisappointment online, with some
OL,15,Fsaying they were left "gutted" by the
OL,16,Fdecision.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
