PN,38505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1772701496
OL,3,CPopular Jersey festival cancelled over
OL,4,Cmoney concerns
OL,6,FHowever, most festivalgoers have been
OL,7,Fsupportive and are optimistic for
OL,8,Ffuture events, with one person saying:
OL,9,F"Gutted but totally understandable.
OL,10,FBig love to the Wonky crew."
OL,12,FAnother states: "See you next year,
OL,13,Ftotally understand, look forward to
OL,14,F2027."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/5
